.TH "platform_finish" 9 "platform_finish" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
platform_finish \- Call platform to switch the system to the working state.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" platform_finish
.BI "(int platform_mode "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "platform_mode" 12
Whether or not to use the platform driver.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Use the platform driver to switch the machine to the normal mode of
operation.

This routine must be called after \fBplatform_prepare\fP.
